<div class="tip_number">TIP 153</div>
<div class="tip_contents">
            A low count of red blood cells (anemia) can cause paleness, fatigue, and a rapid pulse with or without shortness of breath. In certain cases you may feel dizzy or pass out. Diagnosing and treating causes of a low blood count can be life-saving.
        </div>

</div>
